**Q:** i want to add more features beyond just the VADER score. like i noticed some viral videos have all caps or exclamation marks. how do i decide what features are worth adding and which ones are just noise?

**A:** Add features that have a theoretical reason to matter based on your research question. Caps ratio (what percentage of letters are uppercase) is justified because it signals emphasis. Exclamation and question mark counts are justified because punctuation signals urgency. Title word count is worth including as a control since length correlates with information density. Has_number (binary, does the title contain digits like "5 ways to...") is justified by the numbered list pattern you likely see in your top videos. Avoid adding features just because you can engineer them.

